entries.femaleVariant: You work one of their convoys, you don't ask questions.
Just do what they say. Keep your trap shut.
Nope, not even a "yeah," girl. They don't like how you breathe, they'll shoot ya.
Come on. Don't need you tellin' me horror stories.
Horror stories? Whattaya think happened to the choom here before you?
We're dime a dozen, girl. Cheaper, even. So keep your head on straight.
